371
0:12:18,2 --> 0:12:20,97
But it all actually exists.


372
0:12:20,97 --> 0:12:22,6
And what I'm going
to talk to you today


373
0:12:22,6 --> 0:12:24,225
about-- being a Google
crowd, I thought


374
0:12:24,225 --> 0:12:26,225
you might be interested
in some software I wrote


375
0:12:26,225 --> 0:12:29,88
to make one part of it
