to throw the particles.


405
0:13:39,47 --> 0:13:44,99
And so that means I needed to
figure out how it gets there.


406
0:13:44,99 --> 0:13:47,5
And it turns out for a point
acceleration, when you just


407
0:13:47,5 --> 0:13:50,23
