0:14:5,52 --> 0:14:7,23
I could not wrap my
head around the math.


417
0:14:7,23 --> 0:14:8,59
I couldn't find
anybody who could


418
0:14:8,59 --> 0:14:9,964
wrap their heads
around the math.


